private class SMPPTest.SMPPTestPDUEventListener
extends SmppObject
implements ServerPDUEventListener

Implements simple PDU listener which handles PDUs received from SMSC. It puts the received requests into a queue and discards all received responses. Requests then can be fetched (should be) from the queue by calling to the method getRequestEvent.

See Also:
Queue, ServerPDUEvent, ServerPDUEventListener, SmppObject
